            <p>This is how I live my life - I train hard, I eat to fuel my sessions (yes this involves chocolate) and I work equally as hard to train my mind.</p>
            <p>I wasn’t always fit, strong and active. I gained a serious amount of weight in 2014 and want you to know that there’s nothing that makes me special - anyone and everyone can achieve an amazing physique. You just need the right tools - and I’ve got you covered with your training and nutrition programs, mindset coaching and more in my TWS Coaching Platform.</p>
            <a class="find-program about-button" href="#">
                <span> your program</span></a>
